~ contract_galsal_1
do BaseDialogueManager.dialogue_activated.emit()
Galsal: Hi, Do you have something to do??
- Yes
	Galsal: You got a job for me?
	- Yes
		Galsal: You got me!
		do proceed_contract()
		
	- Listen to me (Negotiate)
		Galsal: You know what? That sound interesting...
		do try_negotiate_contract()
		do BaseDialogueManager.dialogue_deactivated.emit()
		=> END

	- No
		Galsal: Oh.. okey
		do BaseDialogueManager.dialogue_deactivated.emit() 
		=> END
- No
	Galsal: ...
do BaseDialogueManager.dialogue_deactivated.emit() 
=> END


~ casual_galsal_1
do BaseDialogueManager.dialogue_activated.emit()
Galsal: [[Hi|Hello|Howdy]], this is TEST dialogue.
Galsal: Here are some choices.
- First one
	Galsal: You picked the first one. 
- Second one
	Galsal: You picked the second one.
- Start again => casual_galsal_1
- End the conversation 
	do BaseDialogueManager.dialogue_deactivated.emit() 
	=> END
	
